    },
    {
      '@type': 'Question',
      name: 'Where can I buy organic gummy bears?',
      acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: 'Organic gummy bears are available at Whole Foods (largest in-store selection), Amazon (best multi-pack pricing), Target, Sprouts, Natural Grocers, and most health food stores. YumEarth and Black Forest Organic have the widest distribution and are available at conventional grocery stores including Kroger, Safeway, and Publix.' },
