    </div>

    <p>This guide is part of our <a href="/candy/">vegan gummy candy</a> hub. For non-organic vegan options, see our <a href="/candy/vegan-gummy-bears/">vegan gummy bears</a> guide. For a broader view of all plant-based candy types, visit our <a href="/candy/plant-based-gummy-candy/">plant-based gummy candy</a> overview.</p>

