    <p>Surf Sweets earns "Cleanest Ingredients" because their Organic Fruity Bears have the shortest, most transparent ingredient list of any organic gummy bear we reviewed. Real organic fruit juice is a primary ingredient — not just a flavoring additive — which gives each bear a natural, fruit-forward taste that synthetic flavors cannot replicate. The top 14 allergen-free certification is the broadest in the category, covering tree nuts, peanuts, dairy, eggs, soy, wheat, fish, shellfish, sesame, mustard, celery, lupin, sulfites, and mollusks. This makes Surf Sweets the safest option for school environments with strict allergen policies.</p>

